values:
Today was great!

I got up at like 2 so I didnt even have to think of breakfast :D
I went out and was on my trampoline for 3 hours +

I was really hungry so just had some ice cubes :)
Then my mum was home around 6 and tried to make me have dinner...
I said I wasnt feeling too great so she didnt push it.
My dad was annoying me tho.
He kept saying "whats wrong fatty? MMM this food is great!" 
It just made me more determined :)

Its now 8.40pm and Ive had nothing all day.
I actually feel so great!!! :D
Im going to the gym all day tomorrow aswell :)
Should be good.

X

My mum found out about me visiting this website for support with my ED.
She totally freaked and blocked me from live journal :(
Well I got a laptop for christmas so Im back woo!

Thank god!
I actually have felt so alone the last few months.

Well heres my new stats:
Height:5,6
Hw: 136
Lw: 82
Cw: 85

Things are going goodn for a change.
Im looking forward to the support from the girls : )

Oh if you're from the Uk drop me a message.
I need a txt buddy : )

Think Thin X

Im doing ok today I suppose.

I went shopping with my mum and she made me have fruit salad :[
(58 cals)

Im not having anything tonight.
I feel so fat from eating that fruit :[
Im gonna go to bed I think...
Least if im asleep mum cant make me have dinner

x

I just binged on tomato on toast!

:[

Im so fat! 
No more food today.

x

Today is going great!
Its 12.35pm and ive had nothing to eat.
Ive already done 2 hours on the dance mat which is 720cals (apparanty) - I read it on a website.
Im just getting ready to take my dog a walk - more cals burnt woo!

My mums home early today which means I'll have to eat dinner :[
I could just say im not hungry :/
Afterall nobody expects a fat girl to be anorexic :]

x

This fast is starting to suck.

IM SO HUNGRY!

:[
